data.description: This is a very nice home and will make a great starter home if you're wanting to downsize.  It is a low-maintenance home in a great neighborhood full of friendly people.  This home has two bedrooms on the main floor and a room in the lower level that could be used for anything you would want such as a hobby room or bedroom if you want to go there just to watch TV with a full bath down there, also.  The kitchen has a newer sink (2 years) and all of the appliances are included (2 years).  All-new laminate flooring with an open concept into the dining and living areas.  It is very family-friendly and for your convenience, there is a main floor laundry.  The water heater is 1 year old.  Outside is the garage with a patio between the house and garage.  This is a wonderful house waiting for you to make it your HOME.  Call today for your private showing.
